N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 5.26 - Rejection of lists, replacements and additions

State Regulations

The commission may reject any list, in whole or in part, or
any replacement or addition to any list, if it determines that such list or
part thereof, or any replacement or addition thereto, was not made in
conformance with this Part or in accord with the act. Notes
